# Important Architecture Adjustment

Since Databricks Free Edition cannot directly access your local Docker Kafka:

```text
Your Laptop
 └── Kafka
```

and

```text
Databricks Cloud
```

are separate networks.

So for the next phase we'll simulate Kafka ingestion using files.

### Why This Is Fine

Structured Streaming doesn't care whether the source is:

```text
Kafka
File Stream
Event Hub
Kinesis
```

The concepts are identical:

* Streaming DataFrames
* Checkpointing
* Watermarks
* Stateful Processing

